files..claude-plugin/marketplace.json:
{
  "name": "vibekit",
  "owner": {
    "name": "Agentient"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "description": "AI skills marketplace with advanced reasoning techniques for research, evaluation, and documentation",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "pluginRoot": "./plugins"
  },
  "plugins": [
    {
      "name": "research-tools",
      "source": "research-tools",
      "description": "Research workflow: systematic interviewing → research brief design → multi-source consolidation",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "research",
      "tags": ["research", "interviewing", "MECE", "knowledge-elicitation", "epistemic-tracking"]
    },
    {
      "name": "evaluation-tools",
      "source": "evaluation-tools",
      "description": "Multi-expert evaluation and deliberation patterns for structured analysis",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "evaluation",
      "tags": ["evaluation", "expert-panel", "deliberation", "database-schema", "scoring"]
    },
    {
      "name": "documentation-tools",
      "source": "documentation-tools",
      "description": "Diátaxis-aligned documentation with cognitive load management",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "documentation",
      "tags": ["documentation", "diataxis", "tutorials", "how-to", "cognitive-load"]
    },
    {
      "name": "prompt-tools",
      "source": "prompt-tools",
      "description": "Prompt engineering and optimization for Claude",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "prompts",
      "tags": ["prompts", "optimization", "prompt-engineering"]
    },
    {
      "name": "meta-tools",
      "source": "meta-tools",
      "description": "Generate domain-specific skills using advanced reasoning techniques",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "meta",
      "tags": ["skill-generation", "meta", "templates", "reasoning-techniques"]
    },
    {
      "name": "python-tools",
      "source": "python-tools",
      "description": "Python 3.13 patterns with Pydantic V2, async, pytest, type hints",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "development",
      "tags": ["python", "pydantic", "pytest", "async", "type-hints", "mypy"]
    },
    {
      "name": "adk-tools",
      "source": "adk-tools",
      "description": "Google ADK agent development with Vertex AI SDK",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "agents",
      "tags": ["adk", "vertex-ai", "agents", "orchestration", "rag", "gemini"]
    },
    {
      "name": "frontend-tools",
      "source": "frontend-tools",
      "description": "Next.js 14+, React, TypeScript, Firebase, Tailwind, Zustand patterns",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "frontend",
      "tags": ["nextjs", "react", "typescript", "firebase", "tailwind", "zustand", "shadcn"]
    },
    {
      "name": "gcp-tools",
      "source": "gcp-tools",
      "description": "GCP deployment, Cloud Run, CI/CD, Infrastructure as Code",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "devops",
      "tags": ["gcp", "cloud-run", "cicd", "terraform", "devops"]
    },
    {
      "name": "mcp-tools",
      "source": "mcp-tools",
      "description": "Model Context Protocol server development patterns",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "development",
      "tags": ["mcp", "protocol", "tools", "resources", "asyncio"]
    },
    {
      "name": "quality-tools",
      "source": "quality-tools",
      "description": "Testing, code review, linting, coverage analysis",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "quality",
      "tags": ["testing", "code-review", "linting", "coverage", "quality"]
    },
    {
      "name": "observability-tools",
      "source": "observability-tools",
      "description": "Logging, tracing, error tracking, alerting, OpenTelemetry",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "operations",
      "tags": ["logging", "tracing", "sentry", "opentelemetry", "alerting"]
    },
    {
      "name": "performance-tools",
      "source": "performance-tools",
      "description": "Frontend and backend performance optimization patterns",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "category": "performance",
      "tags": ["performance", "profiling", "caching", "optimization", "bundle"]
    },
    {
      "name": "rag-tools",
      "source": "rag-tools",
      "description": "[STUB] RAG pipeline development with Vertex AI RAG Engine",
      "version": "0.1.0",
      "category": "agents",
      "tags": ["rag", "embeddings", "vertex-ai", "retrieval"]
    },
    {
      "name": "security-tools",
      "source": "security-tools",
      "description": "[STUB] Security audit, OWASP, authentication, compliance",
      "version": "0.1.0",
      "category": "security",
      "tags": ["security", "owasp", "authentication", "compliance"]
    },
    {
      "name": "architecture-tools",
      "source": "architecture-tools",
      "description": "[STUB] C4 diagrams, OpenAPI specs, architectural decisions",
      "version": "0.1.0",
      "category": "architecture",
      "tags": ["c4", "openapi", "mermaid", "adr"]
    }
  ]
}
